{"id": 601, "genre": 1001, "title": "回忆前几年的双十一，你都做过什么蠢事？", "description": "但这并不能阻止我继续做蠢事，啊！迫不及待地想要去做蠢事了！搓手！（题图来自Fast Company）", "record_count": 3159, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194505poEjROAhZybJ8F6I.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-01T01:00:44Z", "options": [{"id": 21509, "content": "去年今日此门中，人面桃花相映红", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278184}, {"id": 21510, "content": "不断的刷图", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252567}, {"id": 21511, "content": "蠢在屯了三年的姨妈巾，可是第二年就怀孕了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 325, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 221802}, {"id": 21515, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229939}, {"id": 21516, "content": "买了一堆注定过期的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237208}, {"id": 21518, "content": "大学时和舍友们脸手机对着手机分裂那几块钱的红包。我一点都不觉得蠢。想她们。现在都是孤军奋战。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278266}, {"id": 21520, "content": "逛街时看到好看的记下货号回头到天猫下单，今年绝对不干这事儿了，已崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278263}, {"id": 21521, "content": "幸好什么都没买?", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277655}, {"id": 21524, "content": "想躺床上逛一天淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278330}, {"id": 21531, "content": "好便宜啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278478}, {"id": 22299, "content": "上网看热闹", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239725}, {"id": 21534, "content": "依然能做到理性消费，不囤积，买必需。多少要便宜的，何必那样吐槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278536}, {"id": 21536, "content": "被骗了两年，今年绝对不会买买买！何必呢！把钱换成一堆货放家里等过期真的好吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278072}, {"id": 21537, "content": "提前买了现实才能穿的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259836}, {"id": 21539, "content": "进不去网购页面，等着它加载等了半宿……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118439}, {"id": 21540, "content": "一天都在跟自己说不买不买  最后一个小时了   买买买   买一堆难看的破烂", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197874}, {"id": 24100, "content": "买了个剃须刀65，一周后同学在京东上买的同款，55?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195048}, {"id": 21542, "content": "买得不够多", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156697}, {"id": 21545, "content": "不冲支付宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278787}, {"id": 21546, "content": "表示对双十一不感兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278864}, {"id": 21550, "content": "该买的没买，不该买的都买", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274853}, {"id": 21551, "content": "明明有女朋友，却说自己是单身狗，结果现在真成了单身?", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211845aD3NSmYB9tAprLZU.jpg", "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278961}, {"id": 21552, "content": "我还以为是光棍节！引以为豪", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278955}, {"id": 21558, "content": "大刀准备好了等待11", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252490}, {"id": 21559, "content": "为了过光棍节，依然坚持单身?", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211539yUiFkJ1zpuwqjXRN.jpg", "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279042}, {"id": 21560, "content": "搂着另外几个单身狗唱k喝酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216032}, {"id": 21561, "content": "从不在双十一买衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272560}, {"id": 21562, "content": "刮红包啊 我朋友挂到100块好不好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237122}, {"id": 21565, "content": "借着双十一买空了购物车", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279109}, {"id": 21566, "content": "写作业啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237259}, {"id": 21567, "content": "买了一顿没用的垃圾。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279185}, {"id": 21569, "content": "双十一么钱购物！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279194}, {"id": 24900, "content": "买的衣服今年都没穿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304677}, {"id": 21573, "content": "买了一大堆东西，剩下一个月只能就着牛奶啃面包，买的东西基本上没动过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251553}, {"id": 21576, "content": "买了好多护肤品 然而收到后发现至少三年不用买新的了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 221751}, {"id": 21577, "content": "今年過單身狗節日咯，分手快樂，祝我找到一個好的吧，人生那麼長，總會遇到一兩個人渣，不要再遇到就行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279391}, {"id": 21578, "content": "一堆想买的，奈何口袋空空，只好都怪每年那天都出差", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279395}, {"id": 21579, "content": "就是想买买买。。其实也不便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279436}, {"id": 21581, "content": "蠢在不知道已经双十一了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196312}, {"id": 21586, "content": "加了一堆东西进购物车然后12点停网了", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279491}, {"id": 27731, "content": "a'", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 320364}, {"id": 21588, "content": "前年双十一买了一件优衣库的爆款羽绒服，至今没穿过一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279504}, {"id": 21590, "content": "双11睡过头, 购物车里的商品都到期。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277966}, {"id": 21591, "content": "买了一堆没用的。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276223}, {"id": 21592, "content": "庆幸双十一打败了光棍节，我的节日还是我的节日。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279603}, {"id": 21593, "content": "诶", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233299}, {"id": 21597, "content": "大一和室友一起吃饭庆祝单身", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211508lFQK20JDkcZ3B4En.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257538}, {"id": 21599, "content": "自以为很！便！宜！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227828}, {"id": 21600, "content": "自以为很！便！宜！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227828}, {"id": 21858, "content": "跟女朋友分手，算么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121848}]}